data.description:
Welcome home to this charming and adorable 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence that exudes warmth and character. Nestled in Country Club Estates, this delightful home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a cozy living space adorned with charming details, inviting natural light, a cozy woodburning fireplace, and beautiful hardwood floors through. One of the highlights of this property is the expansive fenced yard, offering a secure haven for outdoor activities, playtime, and relaxation. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet afternoon, the large yard provides a versatile space for all to enjoy. With its convenient location and numerous charming features, this home is perfect for those seeking a blend of functionality and aesthetics. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful residence your own – schedule a showing today and experience the allure of this charming home.
